ISLAMABAD, Dec 18 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan Saturday expressed condolences to the families of victims of the twin blasts at Sher Shah Paracha Chowk Karachi.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “My heartfelt prayers & condolences go to all the families of victims of the twin blasts at Sher Shah Paracha Chowk, Karachi. I am especially saddened to hear of the loss of our MNA Alamgir Khan’s father who also perished in the blast. May Allah give him strength to bear this loss.”
